Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:47.64,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can't just leave all the\Nwork up to you young'uns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若いもんだけに\N任せておくわけにゃいかないだに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっひっひっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:51.23,utaware def,,0,0,0,,The fence is done, Hakuoro-san!
