Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.27,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Ah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ご苦労さま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.98,utaware def,,0,0,0,,The enemy will be here before long.
