Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.82,utaware def,,0,0,0,,You need to make sure that you\Nget some rest too, Hakuoro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハクオロさんこそ\Nちゃんと休んでくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.28,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Right.
